  "prompt": "Where can I get best quality soft contact lenses in Sydney?",
  "response": "In Sydney, there are several reputable places where you can purchase high-quality soft contact lenses. Here are some options:\n\n1. **Optometrists and Eye Care Clinics**: Visiting an optometrist is often the best option. They can provide personalized fittings and recommendations. Some well-known practices include:\n   - **Specsavers**: Multiple locations across Sydney offering a range of contact lenses.\n   - **David Jones Optical**: Known for quality eyewear and contact lenses, located in various David Jones department stores.\n   - **Sydney Eye Specialists**: Offers a wide range of contact lenses along with comprehensive eye care.\n\n2. **Contact Lens Stores**: There are specialized stores that focus on contact lenses and eye care:\n   - **Contact Lens Store**: Offers a variety of brands and types of contact lenses.\n   - **Vision Direct**: An online retailer that provides a wide selection of contact lenses with home delivery.\n\n3. **Online Retailers**: Sites like **123optical** and **Ozcontacts** can offer competitive pricing and convenience with home delivery options. Make sure to check for your specific prescription before ordering.\n\n4. **Drugstores and Pharmacies**: Some larger chains, like **Chemist Warehouse** and **Priceline**, may have a selection of contact lenses available, though they typically do not offer the same level of professional fittings and personalized care.\n\nBefore purchasing contact lenses, it\u2019s vital to have a proper eye examination and fitting to ensure you choose the right product for your needs. Always consult with an eye care professional for the best advice tailored to your vision requirements.",
